OL,3,CPedestrian taken to hospital after hit
OL,4,Cand run
OL,6,FA pedestrian has been taken to
OL,7,Fhospital after a hit and run in
OL,8,FBristol.
OL,10,FThe collision happened just before
OL,11,F10pm on Saturday 28 March on Coulsons
OL,12,FRoad in Whitchurch.
OL,14,FAvon and Somerset Police believe that
OL,15,Fthe driver did not stop at the scene
OL,16,Fand the force is appealing for
OL,17,Finformation to help trace the vehicle.
OL,19,FOfficers understand that the car was
OL,20,Fbeing driven in the direction of Court
OL,21,FFarm Road from East Dundry Road.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
