OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1774962671
OL,3,CPedestrian taken to hospital after hit
OL,4,Cand run
OL,6,FAvon and Somerset Police said: "The
OL,7,Fdriver failed to stop the car at the
OL,8,Fscene and CCTV enquiries are already
OL,9,Funderway to trace the vehicle and help
OL,10,Fus identify the person involved.
OL,12,F"The pedestrian has been taken to
OL,13,Fhospital where they are continuing to
OL,14,Freceive treatment.
OL,16,F"Witnesses, or anyone who may have
OL,17,Frelevant dashcam, CCTV or doorbell
OL,18,Ffootage, is asked to call 101 and
OL,19,Fquote reference number 5226085673."
